v10.10 — 2026-05-20
General
- Fixed a regression where the tab description panel (title, "?" button, description text) stopped displaying after upgrading from v10.x. Root cause: the migration runner was re-applying v9.x migrations on every v10.x upgrade due to a lexicographic version comparison bug, which overwrote cfg/TabsDescription.xlsx with an outdated version.
- Fixed the migration runner to use file-position-based ordering instead of string comparison, preventing any future re-application of already-applied migrations.

v10.9 — 2026-05-20
General
- Updating the application no longer fails with a file-lock error on Windows: the new JAR is downloaded to a temporary file and then atomically replaces the running one.
- All update steps are now written to updater.log for easier diagnostics when something goes wrong.
- Fixed a data-corruption bug in the updater byte reader that could silently truncate downloaded files.

v10.8 — 2026-05-20
General
- Update check now always fetches the latest version, bypassing CDN cache. Updates to future releases will be detected immediately after release.

v10.7 — 2026-05-20
DataSeeding
- DataSeeding module is now embedded in the main application, ensuring all users run the latest version automatically on update.

v10.6 — 2026-05-20
General
- Tab descriptions now display correctly for all users after upgrading from a previous version.

v10.5 — 2026-05-20
General
